reviews.text: Burgers were juicy. Staff were nice. A little pricey.

Better come at around 9pm and weekday, because less people is queuing.
I came for dessert, there's two types of pancake, souffle or creme brulee. I prefer souffle pancake, the textile is really light and worth to try.
Beside dessert, there's main course as well. Will come and try soon
Stunning food is served here, esp. the creme brulee pancake! Attractive eggy fragrance and light milk cream are the highlights!

Located inside i.t. fashion store in Festival Walk, J.S. Foodies is a newly opened restaurant that sells western cuisines in Japanese style, such as pancakes, souffle pancakes (by Flippers), burgers, and coffee.

Similar to Flippers in Causeway Bay, J.S. Foodies has an interior design with a blue colour tone. I particularly like this massive burger sticker near the bar table.

We ordered a burger and pancake to share between the two of us. This Cheese Burger with caramelized onion is absolutely lovely! The bun was so fluffy with a crispy top, tomato and lettuce were fresh (not that I care as I hate veggies but just so you know :P). The beef patty was loosely held together, probably because it’s home made with fresh minced beef? The cheese was melted right to the point, but the caramelized onion kinda take away its shine. Make sure you ask for caramelized onion (for free) to enjoy your burger to its best flavour. Thick fries are just thick fries, but they were freshly fried and delicious.

We love this Caramel Brownie Pancake with Coffee Ice Cream dearly! It’s such a nice combination to have brownie, pancake and ice cream at the same time as a dessert to satisfy your three cravings. The brownie made a good and moist filling for pancakes. The caramel wasn’t overly sweet and was right to the point to give a sweet scent to the pancake. The coffee ice cream? Fantastic! It’s so enjoyable!! Not to miss out the caramelized nuts on the side, we swiped them clean quickly worrying that the waiters/waitresses would take away our plate before we had a chance to finish them.

It was a nice, filling and satisfying early dinner. The waiting time was just a few minutes when we got there at around 17:30.

Lucky to be able to get in without waiting at the opening hour in the Sunday morning! Signature fluffy pancake is surprisingly good. It is as good as it plainly is without fruit or honey.  
Earl Grey tea is dark and strong with a touch of vanilla scent. It is served with sweet mochi.  Strong tea and sweet delicacy give a nice balance of taste.

新開張，比在銅鑼灣排個半鐘，呢度下午1:30開始排，2:00左右開以入座，並沒限時交枱。薯條漢堡pancake味道不錯，有水準。但上菜速度不快，要細心等候。服務員快手但十分有禮貌。推～～
再encore, 意粉好味幌夠大同新鮮。Pancake都好味，但一人未必食得晒。朱古力frappe 好味，唔太甜。

難得平日六點幾唔需要排隊, 入去叫左個souffle pancake食, 一個人食哂都唔覺溜
服務都幾好, 侍應會不停refill水
來自日本過江龍的JS Foodies估唔到除咗招牌的pancake此外，鹹點也做得十分出色。印度燒雞咖喱飯，咖喱乛⼃⼀香口，而且燒雞亦都做得很滑！
6點到，排左一陣隊，原味pancake 好鬆軟，味道幾好，漢堡包熱辣辣，肉汁多，個包都係熱和跪，用心預備，惟一缺點係上菜較慢。等左30分鐘，6點半後好多人排隊。

result.name: Festival Walk

reviews.text: Good arcade to shop for medium to medium-high end brands in a spacious environment with both restaurants and food court to suit varying tastes of customers. Great parking lot. Multiple sakes receipts accepted for free parking.

Very crowded and very clean like a hospital. Come here on Sunday and you can enjoy waiting for a table for an hour with everyone. Best place if you want to buy a Rolex for $900,000 to go with your yacht sitting in a port in Italy.
Multiple restaurants and shops. A very big mall, and a nice theater to watch movies. The restaurants were also very nice. A very good shopping mall overall.

I like Festival Walk as it is rarely super crowded like the malls at Sha Tin always seem to be. The TASTE supermarket is fantastic here with a range of products from around the world including Waitrose products and a good frozen section. Other stores I like here are Zara Home, Log On, M&S and the Cinema which let's you bring Starbucks in. I sometimes come here to walk around on rainy days too as it is so big and there are very few shoppers with suitcases.

I like Windows shopping here.cause if not people mountain people sea. Can very relaxed to take a look.some shop I used take a look.like hk a female designer. She design Chinese match west.she control color very. Very good. Also one best of world shoe shop. Tecstoni.name may be not correct. It is one of best Italian designer band shoe shop.
